# Module 2: Prompt Engineering for Developers – Facilitator Guide

## ⏱ Timing
60 minutes total
- Bad vs Good Prompt Demo: 10 min
- Prompt Building Activity: 15 min
- Personal Prompt Library Demo: 15 min
- Peer Testing: 10 min
- Emotional/Role Prompting Wrap-up: 10 min

## 👩‍🏫 Key Talking Points
- Importance of context and examples in prompts
- Saving prompts as templates for reuse
- Emotional prompting for specialized roles (security, performance, QA)

## 🛠 Facilitation Tips
- Encourage students to think about their own workflows
- Highlight differences in prompting strategies across tools
